1. *Donio* sam ti poklon za rođendan. (I brought you a gift for your birthday.)
2. On je sinoć *donio* odluku da se preseli u drugi grad. (He made the decision to move to another city last night.)
3. Kada je direktor *donio* odluku o novoj politici, zaposleni su se obradovali. (When the director made the decision about the new policy, the employees were happy.)
4. Njegov izbor je *donio* mnogo problema porodici. (His choice brought a lot of problems to his family.)
5. Naš sastanak će se održati kada *doneseš* odluku o tome. (Our meeting will take place when you make a decision about it.)
6. Ova knjiga mi je *donijela* mnogo radosti tokom teških vremena. (This book brought me a lot of joy during difficult times.)
7. Kada sam *donio* odluku o promjeni karijere, bio sam veoma zabrinut. (When I made the decision to change careers, I was very worried.)
8. Kada su *donijeli* novi zakon, mnogi građani su bili nezadovoljni. (When they brought the new law, many citizens were unhappy.)
9. Molim te, *donesi* mi vodu iz frižidera. (Please bring me some water from the fridge.)
10. *Donosite* li uvijek cvijeće za svoju ženu za Dan zaljubljenih? (Do you always bring flowers for your wife on Valentine's Day?)